name: What you can't see is what you get

metadata.name: What you can't see is what you get (1/8)
metadata.description:
This dynamic NFT changes when connected to TOR. The true content of the NFT is censored on the regular internet, it can only be seen via the TOR browser.

To see your hidden NFT, just copy paste the opensea URL into your connected TOR browser.

We are not responsible if the hidden content is illegal in your country <3
